Description
-----------

The **shear** keyword shears a stage by the given offset.

Usage
-----

    shear [x], [y]

Parameters
----------

-   [x] = The x offset
-   [y] = The y offset

Example
-------

Shear the stage at a constant rate...

    {
       shear time, time
       map   textures/custom/foo.tga
    }

Notes
-----

Not Available.


